{"type": "article", "id": 25018, "title": "Gucci男女装秀将合并，以及，MCM的新印花系列还不错｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-04-06T10:15:26Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 12089, "name": "女装"}, {"id": 6579, "name": "春夏系列"}, {"id": 25880, "name": "金狮奖"}, {"id": 1898, "name": "时装周"}, {"id": 15755, "name": "走秀"}, {"id": 25881, "name": "设计赛"}, {"id": 671, "name": "Gucci"}, {"id": 977, "name": "Tom Ford"}, {"id": 686, "name": "adidas"}, {"id": 1453, "name": "MCM"}, {"id": 4827, "name": "Ermenegildo Zegna"}, {"id": 1980, "name": "Topshop"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 66, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607130451TiH1WsFM7lrOo5VB.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>一些重要的新闻：</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/designer-luxury/gucci-unifies-mens-womens-shows-alessandro-michele-10403532/\"><b>Gucci 男女走秀合并</b></a>｜开云旗下意大利奢侈品牌 Gucci 计划从 2017 年的秀场开始将男装和女装走秀，第一场合并的秀预计在 Gucci 的米兰新总部 Via Mecenate 酒店举办。而 2 月英国奢侈品牌 Burberry 刚刚宣布合并男女装秀。Gucci 创意总监 Alessandro Michele 表示这对他来说是再自然不过的事，将会有更多机会尝试不同类型的 story telling 方式。Gucci 的总裁兼 CEO  Marco Bizzarri 则说“合并将会在很大程度上帮助我们精简业务，传统的两场独立、无关联的秀一点也不实用。“</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://sg.fashionmag.com/news/Topshop-and-Decoded-Fashion-create-start-up-challenge,676082.html#.Vv3KVoQrJQY\"><b>Topshop 为创业者推出新项目</b></a>｜英国时尚零售巨头 Topshop 近日宣布将与 Decoded Fashion 合作，推出专为创业团队、开发商等提供机会的项目 Topshop Challenge，寻求创业者和企业家为 Topshop 想出利用科技去提升购物体验的方式。比赛将于 4 月 22 日开始。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://sg.fashionmag.com/news/Ermenegildo-Zegna-sales-up-profits-down-in-2015,677713.html#rl\"><b>Ermenegildo Zegna 2015 年收入上涨</b></a>｜意大利品牌 Ermenegildo Zegna 最近公布了 2015 年收入上涨了 4% 至 12.61 亿欧元，去年同期呈衰退表现只有 12.1 亿欧元。考虑到不可预见的地理政治因素和经济衰退，公司对于这一结果表现较为满意，利润则从去年同期的 7100 万欧元下跌至 4500 万。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://sg.fashionmag.com/news/Traditional-Chinese-clothing-design-award-begins-in-Beijin,677782.html#rl\"><b>中国华服设计大赛北京举办</b></a>｜首届“继承匠心中国华服设计大赛”最近在北京举办，寻找能够结合中华传统和现代灵感的时尚设计人才，中国纺织品服装协会主办，新华社、新华网和纺织服装周刊联合举办。比赛将持续到 10 月，优秀作品将于 11 月在全国及海外巡回展出。分为业余组和专业组，三位导师，选出 24 位进入决赛选手，最终赢家将获得 15 万人民币。</p>\n<h2>一些值得一看的：</h2>\n<p class=\"\">德国艺术家 Tobias Rehberger 曾获得威尼斯双年展金狮奖，近日为 MCM <a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/4/tobias-rehberger-mcm-collaboration\">合作推出一个几何印花系列包袋</a>：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607130439EfcH8C1djDLTzrXY.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607130439vgtNzjhAZfWXPqEn.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607130440Dr1z6w4gyfYhmbq3.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607130441JDYatoTMPRvCmGUc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607130441CYrUQ1FpZVD5w9f8.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071304421YxB3aNn7mG9zLKo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://bae.hypebeast.com/2016/4/adidas-2016-spring-summer-highlights-lookbook\">Adidas 女装春夏系列</a>，复古感觉的大三叶草 logo ，面料和剪裁是亮点：<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071304427HtDOfNkbGdI6LXx.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75498008\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607130443ZNvCqKORMAgsJIB8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75498008\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071304431VjXvlnTaH03L5Zr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75498008\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607130444sR4STKH8zJEUdmZV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75498008\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">日本男装品牌<a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/4/meagratia-2016-fall-winter\"> Meagratia 2016 秋冬系列 lookbook</a>，简洁的日式美学，经典款带着些创新细节：<br></p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607130444OeyCnJzMK7tPcgd6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75537939\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607130445T5al8URuizLx9327.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75498008\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607130445Xg0Ed4nIZcMKmJs1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75498008\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607130446N7FmdpAiLxzeKSM6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75568182\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">韩国街头品牌 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/4/liful-x-peanuts-collection\"> LIFUL 首个胶囊系列</a>是以 Snoopy 形象为主：<br></p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607130446w4uC89dphqxynbBH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607130447FdsjBHUcRGpm6gY7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607130447msktAjnwcXD6re9y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607130448uN2pmQUZgXbji1k5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">夏天要来了，看看几个品牌出了哪些不错的墨镜？来自<a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/designer-sunglasses-saks-2016-lookbook/\"> Saks Fifth Avenue 精品百货店拍摄的特辑</a>：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide medium-insert-active\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607130449uCvc8sxdPhiJyaqT.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.03\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Tom Ford</div></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607130449lchwzfsob085GMRO.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.03\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Ray-Ban</div></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607130450vSLn1RueATiNrqwx.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.03\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Dolce &amp; Gabbana</div></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071304507rfvPHpXq4YZ5kiC.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.03\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Gucci</div></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607130451GPnU1XxjmV7zhvfY.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.03\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Roberto Cavalli </div></figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><br></p>\n\n\n"}